.TH "LIGHTNING-PAYMENT-STATUS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-payment-status \- check the status of an outbound payment
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning payment-status
.I payment_hash
.SH DESCRIPTION
Looks up an outbound payment by its payment hash and returns its current status.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"payment_hash":"...","status":"complete|failed|pending",
 "amount_msat":N,"fee_msat":N,"destination":"...","created_at":N}
.fi
Returns
.nf
{"error":"not_found"}
.fi
when no matching payment exists.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-payment-list (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-status (1)
